comments: Finney-Smith (DAL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mann (OKC) and firms up to absorb the contact.
Brunson (DAL) makes contact with Mann's (OKC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) legally contests Hardaway Jr. (DAL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Doncic (DAL) makes contact to the body of Wiggins (OKC) on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Giddey (OKC) absorbs the body contact by Hardaway Jr. (DAL) during his shot attempt near the rim.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) jumps from point A to point B but the contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is marginal and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Giddey (OKC) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Muscala (OKC) and his teammate Giddey (OKC) engage and the ball is dislodged.
Mann (OKC) makes contact to Brunson's (DAL) arm as he secures the ball.
Doncic (DAL) avoids making contact with Jerome's (OKC) arm during his shooting motion on the jump shot attempt.
Muscala (OKC) commits a take foul on Green (DAL).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes contact to the arm of Muscala (OKC) that affects his ability to get to the pass.
